---
// src/pages/case-studies.astro
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";

const calendlyUrl = "https://calendly.com/production-sherpamedia/30min";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Case Studies"
  description="Explore how Sherpa Media turns podcast strategy into measurable growth."
>
  <section class="case-studies-page">
    <div class="container">

      <header class="case-page-intro">
        <p class="kicker">Case Studies</p>
        <h1 class="subpage-title">Case Studies</h1>
        <p>Explore how we turn podcast strategy into measurable growth through editing, distribution, and content repurposing.</p>
      </header>

      <div class="case-study-list">

        <!-- ── Hexaware ───────────────────────────── -->
        <article class="case-study-block">
          <div class="case-study-media" aria-hidden="true">
            <video class="case-study-video-bg" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata"
              poster="/assets/img/podcasts/ceo-tech-live.jpg">
              <source src="/assets/videos/case-study-hexaware.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            </video>
          </div>

          <header class="case-study-hero">
            <div class="case-study-visual case-study-visual--award">
              <img class="case-study-avatar" src="/assets/img/podcasts/ceo-tech-live.jpg" alt="CEO Tech Live artwork" />
              <img class="case-study-award" src="/assets/img/awards/marcom-hexaware.png" alt="MarCom award badge" />
            </div>
            <div class="case-study-title-wrap">
              <h2 class="case-study-title">CEO TECH LIVE by HEXAWARE wins <span>GOLD</span> at the MARCOM AWARDS</h2>
              <p class="case-study-subtitle">out of <strong>325,000+</strong> AMCP Entries</p>
            </div>
          </header>

          <div class="case-study-copy-grid">
            <section class="case-study-copy">
              <h3>The Goal</h3>
              <p>Hexaware needed a way to <strong>highlight executives from organizations that have partnered with them for professional services and skilled talent solutions</strong>, demonstrating the real operational impact of those collaborations. Together, we identified a <strong>podcast series as the most effective format</strong> to create space for meaningful leadership conversations and authentic industry insights.</p>
              <p>Sherpa Media partnered with Hexaware to <strong>produce the CEO Tech Live Podcast</strong>, turning these executive discussions into a compelling video-led series that communicates both expertise and partnership value.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="case-study-copy">
              <h3>Our Role</h3>
              <p>For the past <strong>two seasons</strong> with a third on the way, Sherpa Media has worked closely with Hexaware to shape and elevate the show's video presence. We transformed executive conversations into <strong>engaging, brand-aligned content</strong>, handling editing, visual storytelling, and optimization for digital platforms.</p>
              <p>The series is produced in collaboration with <strong>renowned host, leadership speaker, and long-term Sherpa Media client Ben Fanning</strong>, ensuring thoughtful and consistent executive dialogue.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="case-study-copy">
              <h3>The Impact</h3>
              <p>The podcast recently earned <strong>Gold at the 2025 MarCom Awards</strong>, recognized for Industry-Focused Series excellence. The recognition reflects what happens when the right leaders come together for meaningful executive dialogue: conversations that are thoughtful, impactful, and never rushed.</p>
            </section>
          </div>
        </article>

        <!-- ── Fidium ─────────────────────────────── -->
        <article class="case-study-block">
          <div class="case-study-media case-study-media--fidium" aria-hidden="true">
            <video class="case-study-video-bg" autoplay muted loop playsinline preload="metadata"
              poster="/assets/img/podcasts/fidium.jpg">
              <source src="/assets/videos/case-study-fidium.mp4" type="video/mp4" />
            </video>
          </div>

          <header class="case-study-hero case-study-hero--fidium">
            <div>
              <img class="case-study-avatar" src="/assets/img/podcasts/fidium.jpg" alt="Fidium logo" />
            </div>
            <div class="case-study-title-wrap">
              <h2 class="case-study-title">Fidium Fiber Rebrand</h2>
              <p class="case-study-subtitle">Entering the fiber internet market with ease</p>
            </div>
          </header>

          <div class="case-study-copy-grid case-study-copy-grid--narrow">
            <section class="case-study-copy">
              <h3>The Challenge</h3>
              <p>As a legacy telecommunications company entering the fiber internet market, Fidium Fiber needed to introduce a new brand while building trust in rural American communities that have historically been underserved by high-speed infrastructure. The rebrand messaging needed to resonate with investors, future customers, and employees, creating confidence both externally and internally.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="case-study-copy">
              <h3>Our Approach</h3>
              <p>Sherpa Media partnered with Fidium Fiber to bring the rebrand to life through video storytelling. We developed the #BreakthroughLeaders series, producing an 8-episode executive video series, 40 employee testimonial videos, and a brand overview video that captured leadership vision and the people behind the service.</p>
              <p>By showcasing voices across the organization from executives to installers, the content helped communicate Fidium's transition into a fiber-focused provider committed to connecting rural communities.</p>
            </section>

            <section class="case-study-copy">
              <h3>The Impact</h3>
              <p>Strategic video storytelling positioned Fidium Fiber as a trusted, human-centered brand, supporting employee alignment, investor confidence, and stronger connection with new customers during the rebrand.</p>
            </section>
          </div>
        </article>

        <div class="case-page-cta">
          <a class="btn" href={calendlyUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener">BOOK A CALL</a>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .case-studies-page {
    padding-top: 170px;
    padding-bottom: 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 1099px) { .case-studies-page { padding-top: 146px; } }
  @media (max-width: 767px)  { .case-studies-page { padding-top: 124px; } }

  .case-page-intro {
    max-width: 1020px;
    margin-bottom: 68px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .case-page-intro { margin-bottom: 44px; } }
  .case-page-intro p { margin: 0; max-width: 980px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; color: #ebebed; }

  /* ── Case study list ────────────────────────── */
  .case-study-list { display: grid; gap: 84px; }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .case-study-list { gap: 58px; } }

  /* ── Each block ─────────────────────────────── */
  .case-study-block {
    position: relative;
    isolation: isolate;
    overflow: hidden;
    padding: 0 0 54px 0;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .case-study-block { padding-bottom: 40px; } }

  /* Left-to-right gradient overlay that keeps text readable */
  .case-study-block::before {
    content: "";
    position: absolute; inset: 0; z-index: -1;
    background: linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(6,13,27,1) 0%, rgba(6,13,27,.9) 40%, rgba(6,13,27,.28) 100%);
  }

  /* ── Background video ───────────────────────── */
  .case-study-media {
    position: absolute;
    right: -256px; top: 0;
    height: 1280px;
    overflow: hidden;
    opacity: .42;
    filter: saturate(.9);
    z-index: -2;
  }
  .case-study-media--fidium { top: 160px; opacity: .36; }

  @media (max-width: 1099px) {
    .case-study-media { right: -220px; width: min(90vw, 880px); }
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .case-study-media { top: 320px; right: -180px; width: 115vw; height: 360px; opacity: .28; }
    .case-study-media--fidium { top: 320px; opacity: .22; }
  }

  .case-study-video-bg { width: 100%; height: 100%; object-fit: cover; display: block; }

  /* ── Hero (image + title row) ───────────────── */
  .case-study-hero {
    display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 24px; margin-bottom: 26px;
  }
  .case-study-hero--fidium { margin-top: 40px; }

  @media (max-width: 767px) {
    .case-study-hero { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; gap: 18px; }
    .case-study-hero--fidium { margin-top: 24px; }
  }

  /* Circular podcast image */
  .case-study-visual {
    position: relative; width: 316px; height: 316px; flex: 0 0 416px;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .case-study-visual { width: 220px; height: 220px; flex-basis: 220px; } }

  .case-study-avatar {
    width: 316px; height: 316px; border-radius: 50%; object-fit: cover;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .case-study-avatar { width: 220px; height: 220px; } }

  /* Award badge overlaid on the circle */
  .case-study-award {
    position: absolute; top: 20px; right: -8px; width: 200px; height: auto;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .case-study-award { width: 126px; right: -18px; top: 18px; } }

  .case-study-title-wrap { max-width: 720px; }

  .case-study-title {
    margin: 0;
    font-size: clamp(34px, 4.5vw, 48px);
    line-height: 1.06; letter-spacing: -0.01em; font-weight: 900;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .case-study-title { font-size: 35px; } }
  .case-study-title span { color: #ffc300; }

  .case-study-subtitle {
    margin: 8px 0 0; font-size: clamp(26px, 3vw, 32px);
    line-height: 1.15; font-weight: 300;
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .case-study-subtitle { font-size: 28px; } }
  .case-study-subtitle strong { font-weight: 900; }

  /* ── Copy grid ──────────────────────────────── */
  .case-study-copy-grid { width: min(100%, 700px); display: grid; gap: 28px; }
  .case-study-copy-grid--narrow { width: min(100%, 680px); }

  .case-study-copy h3 {
    margin: 0 0 8px; font-size: 32px; line-height: 1.3; font-weight: 900;
    text-shadow: 0 1px 16px rgba(23,113,255,.45);
  }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .case-study-copy h3 { font-size: 30px; } }

  .case-study-copy p { margin: 0 0 10px; font-size: 18px; line-height: 24px; color: #ebebed; }
  .case-study-copy p:last-child { margin-bottom: 0; }
  .case-study-copy strong { font-weight: 800; }

  /* ── Bottom CTA ─────────────────────────────── */
  .case-page-cta { padding-bottom: 90px; }
  @media (max-width: 767px) { .case-page-cta { padding-bottom: 72px; } }
</style>
